column2: SELECT o.ra, o.dec, q.EW_Hb_#, q.Flux_Hb_#, q.redshift, p.lumdist into mydb.exclu_#_ew_Flux_hb_nov2#_# FROM MyDB.exclu_#_info2 AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObjall AS o ON n.objid = o.objid JOIN emissionlinesport as q ON o.specobjid = q.specobjid JOIN Photoz AS p ON o.objid = p.objid
